Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  : 'Browse shops, place orders, and enjoy delicious meals from your favorite campus eateries.'
Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  : 'Log in to browse shops, place orders, and enjoy delicious meals from your favorite campus eateries.'}
